Hey there creators! We're ecstatic to announce that our #feelitreelitbrunch, which we've been organising and anticipating for WEEKS will finally take place on Sunday July 24th at The Barrel & Co., Andheri West! 🥳

This is a first-of-its-kind content creation party hosted by @maliniagarwal and @soul_kari where we will get together over yummy food and cocktails - CREATE content, COLLABORATE and CONNECT as a community! 🤩

An event tailored for creators to get together and simply CREATE epic collabs, what an idea, haina?! 💖 All you have to do is drop us a comment with the kind of reels you want to make at the event - DANCE, ENTERTAINMENT, FOOD, FASHION, BEAUTY etc - choose your adventure! Once you comment we'll DM you a link to get your tickets! 🎫

Don't forget to tag your friends so they can come too and join the Good Creator Co. Facebook Group so you never miss a Good Creator Co. party!

We hope y’all are as excited as us cause in the words of Barney Stinson, it’s going to be “LEGEND wait for it…….. DARY” 😂

Hey creators, it’s time for the fun weekly DP contest that we have for all you talented creators out there 🥳 

As you know, we at The Good Creator Co are all about providing a stepping stone for all you creators out there and this contest is another way of us showing our appreciation to you. 

All you have to do for this is, describe your account, what the idea behind it is and what it represents and we will choose one interesting creator story who will get a chance to be the face of our page for a day!

Doesn’t that sound exciting? So, let's get started ⭐️

Contest Alert 🔔 drop a comment if you’d like to read a copy of my book I will send 10 signed copies out along with my personally curated and designed annual planners to you as a special gift! Don’t forget to mention your city in the comments too and share this post with an avid reader or anyone keen to explore a career in social media 🚀📔 

Excited to take my second book, @undertheinfluence, on a little Lit Fest circuit this year, starting with @hindulitforlife in Chennai and then @keralalitfest, Kerala! 📚✨ I can’t wait to meet some incredible local creators from these vibrant cities and connect over stories, creativity, and all things inspiring. If you’d like to meet up, drop a comment with your city—I’d love to know where you’re from! 🌟💬

A huge thank you to everyone who has supported my book so far—your love and encouragement mean the world to me, and I’m so grateful to have gone on this incredible journey with all of you. 💖

Let’s make this year all about storytelling, creativity, and unforgettable moments! 💫
